              <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics1-61ef.png" id="id1166489989007__onlineimage" height="151" width="465"/>
            </media>
          </figure>
          <list id="id1166489989034" list-type="bulleted">
            <item>Elke paar, bv. 1 + 100 of 3 + 98, se somtotaal is 101. Daar is 50 pare in totaal. Die som is dus 50 × 101 = 5 050. Maklik, né!</item>
          </list>
